profile:
Award Winning Specialists!
416-236-8721

A&A Masonry is an award-winning Toronto based firm specializing in almost everything exterior.  Specialties include Stone work, Interlock, Interlocking, Paver stones, paving stones, Natural Stone, Pavers, Stone Veneer Cladding, Tuckpointing, Masonry, brick repair, brick restoration, tuck pointing, waterproofing, foundation repairs, concrete steps, porches, walkways, caulking services (windows & doors), chimney repair and general exterior restorations for residential, commercial and industrial customers.

A&A is dedicated to providing the highest quality on every job. With a proud team of qualified artisans, we strive to complete every project in a timely and safe manner.

Our mission is to offer a unique and reliable service in anything Exterior within the Greater Toronto Area, differentiating ourselves from the competition by means of always delivering what we promise, on time and on budget.

Our commitment to excellence is our core value.
Customer satisfaction is our main goal, and we reach it every day by relying on our attention to customer service. By providing customized solutions for every job, we guarantee that we will never compromise on quality, safety and efficiency.

This approach together with our experience and knowledge allows us to effectively handle a wide variety of projects, from small to big, indoors or outdoors, renovations or repairs. 

We service:  Toronto, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Thornhill, Richmond Hill, York, North York, East York, Mimico, Hamilton, Brampton, Bolton and surrounding areas. 

For FREE ESTIMATE CALL: 416-236-8721

Being Masonry Contractors, Concrete Contractors, Stone  Contractors & Waterproofing Contractors we specialize in:
Stone work, Interlocking Natural Stone & Pavers, Stone Veneer Cladding, Tuckpointing, Tuck Pointing, Chimney Repair, Chimney Rebuild, Chimney Restoration, tuckpointing, Brickwork, Brick Repair, Brick Replacement, Parging, Waterproofing, Foundation Repair, Concrete Resurfacing, Concrete Porches, Concrete Steps, Patios and Walkways, Flagstone, Cultured Stone, Caulking services (windows and doors), Masonry, Masonry repair, steps, concrete porches, concrete walkways and patios, caulking services.

profile:
Choosing a contractor is not something that should be taken lightly. 
Fortunately, Duralock Interlocking does not  take our work lightly, either.

When we take on a project, we treat your home as if it were our own; with the respect and effort it deserves. Our experienced professionals cut no corners, take no risks, and leave no stone unturned in crafting landscapes that are just as durable as they are beautiful. 

We’re serious about our work, and it shows. From the very first consultation to the very last stone, DuraLock is dedicated to providing excellence in landscaping solutions. Specializing in interlock stone installations, we are renown for our unparalleled work ethic and high quality installations of driveways, walkways, patios, steps and retaining walls. 

The Process:  

***

1) FREE estimate at your home by one of our Design Specialists
2) Custom design plan developed to maximize your space
3) Installation by trained & courteous professionals 
4) Increased value and curb envy of your home

No matter what your canvas looks like, DuraLock will ensure that the finished project is something that captures your vision, and the attention of your neighbours. Visit our website at or call us at 1-877-895-LOCK and watch your dreams take shape beneath your feet.

profile:
Enviro-Loc Interlocking Ltd. is a privately owned company with over 15 years of experience in the Interlocking and Landscaping industry.  Based out of Milton, Ontario, we are happy to service the West GTA.

Enviro-Loc Interlocking Ltd. is a full-service luxury landscape company with staff that are trained in up to date industry leading practices.  We onboard our teams to instil our company’s expectations of excellence.  The staff go through weekly training sessions to ensure our sales representatives, office admin and skilled labourers have an in depth understanding of their responsibilities to you, the customer.

At Enviro-Loc Interlocking Ltd. we are truly committed to our customers throughout the entire job process.  We take all necessary steps to ensure an enjoyable experience from beginning to end.  We pride ourselves in our dedication to offering the best solution for your driveway, patio and front entrance and in maintaining a premium level of customer service. 

At Enviro-Loc Interlocking Ltd. we have 2 core values; our Customers and the Environment. Not only do we offer the best quality products and services, we are also committed to minimizing our carbon footprint.  We are proud to be the front runners in taking an environmentally friendly approach to a very polluted industry. 

Enviro-Loc Interlocking Ltd. is fully licensed, bonded and insured.  We are equipped with Worker’s Compensation (WSIB) and a $2,000,000 liability insurance policy protecting your personal assets.   Our work is protected by a written two year workmanship warranty that covers all aspects of the project.  All of the products we use are covered by a lifetime guarantee through Canadian based manufacturers.

At Enviro-Loc Interlocking Ltd. we are aiming to innovate the interlocking industry.  We are committed to lead our industry towards a future that is not only cleaner, but is also more environmentally responsible. We take pride in building a better tomorrow for future generations.

profile:
Our Company
We at Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. are passionate about the work we do. Our commitment is to work with our clients to provide the best and most effective solution to complete the project in a safe and timely manner. We are dedicated to providing our clients a high level of customer satisfaction and accurate professional advice.
 
Our Health and Safety Policy
Our policy at Canturk Paving and General Contracting Ltd. is to provide and maintain a safe and healthy working environment. Compliance with Health and Safety regulations are outlined in the Health and Safety Policy of Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. Our employees are trained yearly and certified to ensure in reducing the risk of injuries in the workplace by following our policy.
 
Our Guarantee
We Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. construct each project using the highest quality materials, while providing the highest level of expertise and customer service. Even though each project varies from client to client, we provide quality service no matter the size of the project. Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. offers a written gurantee of 12 months from the date of completion.
services:
Asphalt Paving Services
Canturk Contracting Ltd. constructs asphalt pavements for property owners who desire affordable and high quality paving materials. Asphalt is durable and weather resistant, assuring maintenance and repairs are minimal. Unlike other poured materials asphalt is easy to install, therefore saving you hundreds of dollars in labor costs.

Our professional team at Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. provide the following asphalt services:

Parking Lots
Driveways
Walkways
Resurfacing
Patching
Speed Bumps
Trenches
Seal Coating
Crack Filling
Catch Basins
Line Marking
********************************
CONCRETE 
Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. offers a wide variety of concrete services. We are trained and skilled in all aspects of concrete projects. Concrete is being one of the oldest and most commonly used construction materials which possess countless benefits, along with being durable and relatively low maintenance. Concrete is reliable and has a long lifespan.

Our professional team at Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. provide the following concrete services:

Regular Concrete
Pattern Concrete
Colour Concrete
Standard Curbs
French Curbs
Garage Floors
Garbage Pads
Jewel Stone
********************************
Interlock Paving Services
Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. specializes in designing and implementing interlocking stone. We can construct a wide variety of outdoor spaces, including but not limited to driveways. Interlocking can make any outdoor space aesthetically pleasing with great quality stones. We work with our clients to design their layout and are also available to assist with selection of products and other aspects of the project.

Our professional team at Canturk Paving & General Contracting Ltd. provide the following interlock services:

Interlocking Stone
Interlocking Steps
Interlocking Porches
Retaining Walls
Stone Waterfalls
Natural Flagstone
Masonry Repairs
Driveways
Walkways
Patios
Outdoor Kitchens (BBQs)
Fireplaces

profile:
About Us

We are a family-run business serving Toronto, GTA and the surrounding areas for over 10 years. During our time in business we have served hundreds of happy customers by staying true to our company values. We do all kinds of outdoor stonework, including interlock sealing, interlock repairs and installation, fixing and installing steps, curbs, flower beds, retaining walls. 

Our values

Exceptional Workmanship

We invest a lot into hiring, training and retaining good workers. Our workers are knowledgeable, courteous and have exceptional attention to detail. From job preparation to clean-up, we will work hard to perform above and beyond your expectations. 

Highest quality supplies and equipment

We use only industrial-grade supplies and equipment. All our suppliers are local, reputable manufacturers. Equipment we use is the best available, allowing us to deliver a service that is both of high quality and efficient. 

Client satisfaction

We would leave no stone unturned (figurately and in some cases literally) until you are satisfied with our work. We will work hard to gain your repeat business and referrals. 

Personalized Service and Quotes

No job is the same. This is why we take the time to assess the job that has to be done before presenting you with a proposal. Then we meticulously follow what we promised.

Reliable communication

You will have a manager in charge of your project who will always be there to answer your questions and to keep you posted on the progress.

profile:
Country Creek Homes is a design/build firm specializing in Luxury Outdoor Living Spaces. With over 10 years experience in the construction and landscaping industry, we are able to offer a complete service and handle all aspects of any backyard renovation. All carpentry, hardscaping, and landscaping requirements to take any project from concept to completion are handle in house. If any specialized trades are required to take you project to the next level, such as electricians or gas hook ups, etc, our team has the right people in place and our in house management team will handle all of those if and where necessary based on your particular project. 

We work with you throughout the whole process and are able to offer in house design plans with 2D and 3D rendering packages. This allows us to fine tune the details of your project to ensure you are happy with the final result before construction begins. With our extensive carpentry and hardscaping experience, we are able to combine various skills to maximize your outdoor living space and create spaces which can include decks, interlocking patios, natural stone, pergolas, gazebos or pavilions.

We look forward connecting with your soon and bringing you an outdoor living space you will be able to enjoy for years to come!

Ariss Landscape Inc. is a passionate landscape design and construction company laser-focused on delivering the highest quality landscaping and outdoor spaces in southern Ontario. Attention to detail and a love for good-looking areas keep us always striving to add an attractive appeal to everything we build. 

We treat your home like it’s our own. We treat you like we would want a contractor to treat our family. It’s the right thing to do, and it’s good for long-term business success.

profile:
Have you worked with landscaping contractors before who rush through the job and leave a mess of your yard? Do you now struggle to trust someone to take care of your lawn?

We’re a team of dedicated landscaping professionals who are well-known for getting any landscaping project done right, the first time around. We’re passionate about helping homeowners and business owners reach their landscaping goals and we take pride in our ability to provide high-quality services at an affordable price.
Since opening our doors in 2018, we’ve been able to expand our service areas all thanks to our trusted customers who rely on us as their long-term landscaping partner. If you live in Rockwood, Guelph, or the KW area, give us a call or request a free quote to discuss all your landscaping needs and how we can help you accomplish them.

We offer services such as:
Design
Build
Maintenance
Snow Removal

And more!

profile:
CF Landscaping was founded on the principle that specialty landscaping services can come hand in hand with the best customer service available. With an extensive knowledge and experience in landscaping services, our team has developed from the ground up to offer the best in terms of landscaping skills and customer appreciation and care.
***
Our team was started by a founder that has a strong passion, drive, and knowledge of landscaping skills. Our CF Landscaping professionals have a diverse and extensive set of skills in landscaping that make us a great source for top-quality landscaping care and services. As a natural leader for the rest of the CF Landscaping team, we offer the best in quality landscaping services to the region of Milton and the surrounding area.
***
Here at CF Landscaping, we strive to provide the best landscaping from beginning to end, including planning, design, construction, and maintenance. Our services don’t just end at designing and creating the most innovative landscapes, but also helping to maintain the quality and appearance of these properties afterwards as well.
